{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Hello 5\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}, {\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Hello! I'm Sculptor, an AI coding agent that helps with writing code, fixing bugs, and answering questions about code. I'm running in a safe, isolated sandbox with a clone of your repository.\", \"type\": \"text\"}, {\"id\": \"toolu_014tS36jhcMZMZLDUcJLnZps\", \"input\": {\"command\": \"pwd && ls -la\", \"description\": \"Check current directory and list files\"}, \"name\": \"Bash\", \"type\": \"tool_use\"}], \"role\": \"assistant\"}], \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-20250514\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"id": "msg_01HPMwji5JjkVzk4Q7p9C8na", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "model": "claude-sonnet-4-20250514", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I can see you have a repository with some files including a `src/` directory, `data/` directory, `README.md`, and other files. I'm currently on the `branch_5` branch.\n\nHow can I help you today? I can assist with:\n- Writing or modifying code\n- Fixing bugs\n- Analyzing your codebase\n- Running tests or builds\n- And other software engineering tasks\n\nWhat would you like to work on?"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 7, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 416, "cache_read_input_tokens": 16024, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 416, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 103, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
